21 Sec. 6. (1) "Center program" means a program operated by a
22 district or by an intermediate district for special education
23 pupils from several districts in programs for pupils with autism
24 spectrum disorder, pupils with severe cognitive impairment, pupils
25 with moderate cognitive impairment, pupils with severe multiple
26 impairments, pupils with hearing impairment, pupils with visual
