1 (A) Except as otherwise provided in this sub-subparagraph, the
2 pupil and the teacher of record or mentor complete a 2-way
3 interaction for 1 course during the week on which pupil membership
4 count day or supplemental count day, as applicable, occurs, and the
5 3 consecutive weeks following that week. However, if a school break
6 is scheduled during any of the weeks described in this sub-
7 subparagraph that is 4 or more days in length or instruction has
