17 subparagraph must be to the communication initiated by the teacher
18 of record or mentor, and not some other action taken. This
19 interaction may occur through, but is not limited to, means such as
20 email, telephone, instant messaging, or face-to-face conversation.
21 A parent- or legal-guardian-facilitated 2-way interaction is
