17 (i) If operations begin before the pupil membership count day
18 for the fiscal year, membership is the average number of full-time
19 equated pupils in grades K to 12 actually enrolled and in regular
20 daily attendance on the pupil membership count day for the current
21 school year and on the supplemental count day for the current
22 school year, as determined by the department and calculated by
23 adding the number of pupils registered for attendance on the pupil
