22 the funds for all of the following:
23 (a) Creating an infrastructure that effectively manages the
24 movement of data between data systems used by intermediate
25 districts, districts, and other educational organizations in
26 Michigan based on common data standards to improve student
27 achievement.
28 (b) Utilizing the infrastructure to put in place commonly
29 needed integrations, reducing cost and effort to do that work while
CRM S06118'26 (S-1) sg57ap

127
1 increasing data accuracy and usability.
2 (c) Promoting the use of a more common set of applications by
