6 network.
7 (e) Ensuring local control of data, data security, and student
8 data privacy.
9 (f) Utilizing the infrastructure to promote the actionable use
10 of data through common reports and dashboards that are consistent
11 statewide.
12 (g) Creating a governance model to facilitate sustainable
13 operations of the infrastructure in the future, including
